<Algorithm code="         1. Let _success_ be ? &lt;emu-meta effects=&#34;user-code&#34;&gt;_O_.[[DefineOwnProperty]]&lt;/emu-meta&gt;(_P_, _desc_).         1. If _success_ is *false*, throw a *TypeError* exception.         1. Return ~unused~.       ">
   <head>
